Body: Description: we are trying to import the license and getting the error saying that "Import Failed! Please use a valid license file."

What We've Learned Updated: 07-05 Customer encounter an issue with their EPP license.
The license is registered to Seychelles Ministry of Local Government and Community Affairs.

08-05 We wanted to schedule a remote session and sent them the meeting timeframes.

09-05 Customer returned that now the license is imported.

Next Steps Updated: 07-05 requested more details regarding the issue.

08-05 sent them the proposal for the remote session.

09-05 waiting for their confirmation that the license is working and assigning correctly.
